Package hu.bme.mit.theta.core.dsl.gen

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoreDslListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CoreDslParser.
    CoreDslVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by CoreDslParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoreDslBaseListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of CoreDslListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
    CoreDslBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of CoreDslVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
